---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionHero from '@components/ui/SectionHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Insights"
  description="Published research from ZAI Institute on AI readiness, AI skills, and agent readiness in the enterprise."
>
  <SectionHero
    eyebrow="Insights"
    title="The gap, measured."
    lede="Everyone talks about what AI will do. We study what it actually delivers. Reports informed by structured interviews with senior operators across the institute's executive community. Free to read, no registration."
  />

  <section class="bg-paper text-ink">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-24">

      <div class="max-w-prose-wide mb-16 space-y-4 text-body text-ink/90">
        <p>
          The institute publishes the work it considers most useful to the broader field. Each
          report draws on direct survey responses from the executives in the network, paired with
          the qualitative interviews that anchor the research.
        </p>
        <p>
          New reports release as the work supports them. The finding that holds across the
          published library so far: the strategy gap is wider than the skills gap.
        </p>
      </div>

      <hr class="rule-gold opacity-60 mb-12" />

      <ul class="divide-y divide-light-border/60 list-none p-0 m-0" role="list">

        <li class="py-8 md:py-12 first:pt-0">
          <article class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
            <div class="md:col-span-3">
              <div class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wide-cap text-muted">Report</div>
              <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted mt-1">March 2026</div>
              <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted mt-1">14 min read</div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-9">
              <h2 class="font-display text-h2 text-ink">The AI readiness gap</h2>
              <p class="mt-4 text-body text-ink/90 max-w-prose-wide">
                The gap between what executives expect from AI and what their organizations can
                deliver. How Fortune 500 leaders turn awareness into capability, and where intent
                outruns readiness.
              </p>
              <a
                href="/insights/ai-readiness-gap-2026-updated.html"
                class="inline-block mt-5 text-sm font-medium text-gold-deep border-b border-gold pb-0.5 hover:text-ink"
              >
                Read the report &rsaquo;
              </a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </li>

        <li class="py-8 md:py-12">
          <article class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
            <div class="md:col-span-3">
              <div class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wide-cap text-muted">Report</div>
              <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted mt-1">April 2026</div>
              <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted mt-1">12 min read</div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-9">
              <h2 class="font-display text-h2 text-ink">The AI skills gap</h2>
              <p class="mt-4 text-body text-ink/90 max-w-prose-wide">
                Everyone assumes the gap is skills. The data says otherwise: forty-seven percent of
                leaders name an undefined AI strategy, not a skills shortage, as the barrier between
                what AI promises and what it delivers.
              </p>
              <a
                href="/insights/ai-skills-gap-2026.html"
                class="inline-block mt-5 text-sm font-medium text-gold-deep border-b border-gold pb-0.5 hover:text-ink"
              >
                Read the report &rsaquo;
              </a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </li>

        <li class="py-8 md:py-12">
          <article class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
            <div class="md:col-span-3">
              <div class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wide-cap text-muted">Report</div>
              <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted mt-1">May 2026</div>
              <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted mt-1">10 min read</div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-9">
              <h2 class="font-display text-h2 text-ink">The agent readiness gap</h2>
              <p class="mt-4 text-body text-ink/90 max-w-prose-wide">
                Enterprises are deploying agents faster than they can govern them. Sixty-nine percent
                are piloting or in production. Thirty-nine percent have a formal oversight policy. The
                gap between deployment and control is the next eighteen months of work.
              </p>
              <a
                href="/insights/agent-readiness-gap-2026.html"
                class="inline-block mt-5 text-sm font-medium text-gold-deep border-b border-gold pb-0.5 hover:text-ink"
              >
                Read the report &rsaquo;
              </a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </li>

        <li class="py-8 md:py-12">
          <article class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
            <div class="md:col-span-3">
              <div class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wide-cap text-gold-deep">Open survey</div>
              <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted mt-1">May 2026</div>
              <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted mt-1">10 questions &middot; ~4 min</div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-9">
              <h2 class="font-display text-h2 text-ink">AI governance and accountability</h2>
              <p class="mt-4 text-body text-ink/90 max-w-prose-wide">
                How organizations oversee, control, and answer for the agents they have put to work:
                the gap between deploying AI and being able to stand behind it. Ten questions,
                anonymous, findings published on this page.
              </p>
              <a
                href="/governance-accountability-survey/"
                class="inline-block mt-5 text-sm font-medium text-gold-deep border-b border-gold pb-0.5 hover:text-ink"
              >
                Contribute to the research &rsaquo;
              </a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </li>

      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-ink text-paper">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-prose-wide">
        <div class="eyebrow mb-6">Commission research</div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-h2 text-paper">A question the public reports do not answer?</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg text-paper/85 max-w-prose-narrow">
          The institute commissions custom research for AI platform vendors, large enterprises, and
          investment firms with a specific decision in front of them. Start with a 20-minute fit call.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/research" class="btn btn-primary">How research works</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-ghost-light">Start a conversation</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
